text: Stéphane Demilly Stéphane Demilly (born 26 June 1963 in Albert, Somme) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents the Somme department, and is a member of the Union of Democrats and Independents. ==References== Category:1963 births Category:Living people Category:People from Albert, Somme Category:Union for French Democracy politicians Category:The Centrists politicians Category:Deputies of the 12th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 15th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Union of Democrats and Independents politicians
